#DESCRIPTION
##  Calculus: Double integrals over rectangles
##ENDDESCRIPTION

## DBsubject(Calculus - multivariable)
## DBchapter(Integration of multivariable functions)
## DBsection(Double integrals over rectangles)
## Date(04/18/2014)
## Institution(Colby College)
